 Here's a simple example of how you can create a modal that shows a chat history with 4 messages, 2 from the bot and 2 from the human user, using HTML and JavaScript:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Chatbot Modal</title>
